reviewText: my first time with this seller.no complaints here.they kept me informed.monkeys paw is a movie i have been looking for.i remember seeing that movie back in the 50s.almost 70yr,and i finally have the movie..thangs again

The House On Marsh Road is worth the price of this dvd by itself. I have looked for this film for quite a while and am glad I finally found a good copy. This dvd is in the PAL format, but fortunately Amazon has a selection of PAL compatible dvd players and adapters.
